<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="tr">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8"><meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Luna AI — Sayfa Bulunamadı</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
  <link rel="icon" href="https://i.imgur.com/X4GG8BF.png" type="image/png">
</head>
<body style="min-height:100vh; display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center; background:var(--bg); background-image:radial-gradient(circle at top, rgba(138,180,248,0.05) 0%, transparent 40%);">
  <div class="card" style="width:100%; max-width:500px; text-align:center; padding:40px;">
    <span class="material-icons-round" style="font-size:80px; color:var(--accent); margin-bottom:16px;">explore_off</span>
    <h1 style="font-size:4rem; font-weight:900; margin-bottom:8px; line-height:1; background:linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent), var(--accent-purple)); -webkit-background-clip:text; -webkit-text-fill-color:transparent;">404</h1>
    <h3 style="font-size:1.4rem; font-weight:600; margin-bottom:12px;">Sayfa Bulunamadı</h3>
    <p style="color:var(--text-2); font-size:0.95rem; line-height:1.6; margin-bottom:32px;">Aradığınız sayfa uzayın derinliklerinde kaybolmuş olabilir veya böyle bir modül henüz inşa edilmedi.</p>
    
    <div style="display:flex; justify-content:center; gap:16px;">
      <button class="btn btn-outline" onclick="window.history.back()">
        <span class="material-icons-round">arrow_back</span> Geri Dön
      </button>
      <a href="/" class="btn btn-filled">
        <span class="material-icons-round">rocket_launch</span> Ana Sayfa
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
